file structure

/
/bin --- command program for commands like ls ,cp etc,. are present in this directory.
/sbin --- system level programs like shutdown, reboot, etc.,
/boot -- booting releated data.
/dev --- device parts
/etc  --- configuration 
/home
/lib, /lib64
/media ---external divices or mounts (automatically mount) 
/mnt -- manual mount
proc, sys, users
/opt -- third party softwares
/tmp -- temparary
/var -- logs





